    <item>
      <title>日元再次升值，股市反弹失去动力：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着日元恢复上涨，全球股市上涨势头减弱，在美国劳动力市场出现回弹迹象推动经济出现初步复苏之后，市场对套利交易平仓的担忧再度升温。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 22:20:57 GMT</pubDate>
